# Devanagari Transliterators

Convert among common Devanagari transliteration schemes

Presently it can convert text

decoding from
- Devanagari Unicode
- WX-notation
- Sanskrit Library Phonetic Basic (SLP1)
- International Alphabet for Sanskrit Transliteration (IAST)

encoding to
- Four of the above metioned notations
- (La)Tex notation of IAST diacritics

It has primarily been developed for personal use as a tea-time activity.

Fork the repo on [GitLab](https://gitlab.com/gaudha/devanagari-transliterators). If found bugs, please fix them or raise an issue [here](https://gitlab.com/gaudha/devanagari-transliterators/issues) or report to the [developer](mailto:zombiechum@gmail.com)


